      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 18:38:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷击败对冲基金针对 GDP 挂钩证券提起的诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/argentina-defeats-hedge-fund-suits-over-gdp-linked-securities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷赢得了驳回 Aurelius Capital Management 和其他对冲基金的诉讼，这些诉讼要求支付与南美国家经济表现相关的证券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/argentina-defeats-hedge-fund-suits-over-gdp-linked-securities</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 18:22:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗称以色列对其大院的袭击造成两名将军死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/iran-says-israeli-strike-on-embassy-compound-killed-top-general</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗和叙利亚官方媒体称，以色列对伊朗驻叙利亚大使馆大院发动空袭，造成包括一名高级军事指挥官在内的多人死亡，加剧了这两个长期对手之间的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/iran-says-israeli-strike-on-embassy-compound-killed-top-general</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:55:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>犯罪取代经济成为巴西人最担心的问题，令卢拉不安</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/crime-supplants-economy-as-brazilians-top-worry-rattling-lula</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近几个月来，犯罪问题已成为巴西人最关心的问题，取代经济问题成为他们最关心的问题，并在总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦(Luiz Inacio Lula da Silva)政府内部引发了对如何应对的恐慌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/crime-supplants-economy-as-brazilians-top-worry-rattling-lula</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:36:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新日铁在美国钢铁招标中承诺 2026 年之前不会裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/nippon-steel-makes-formal-pledge-to-union-in-push-for-us-steel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新日铁公司(Nippon Steel Corp.)向美国钢铁工人联合会(United Steelworkers union)做出了所谓的关于支出和就业的正式承诺，支持了早先会议上做出的承诺，因为这家日本钢铁制造商希望为其141亿美元收购美国钢铁公司(United States Steel Corp.)赢得支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/nippon-steel-makes-formal-pledge-to-union-in-push-for-us-steel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:25:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加州绿色城市支持者推进土地所有者法律斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/california-utopian-city-backers-advance-in-landowner-legal-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家为一群试图在加州北部建设可持续城市的科技亿万富翁购买房产的公司赢得了一项裁决，推进了其诉讼，该诉讼指控该项目目标区域的土地所有者合谋抬高价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/california-utopian-city-backers-advance-in-landowner-legal-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:14:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟严厉打击加勒比金护照成本飙升至20万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/caribbean-golden-passport-cost-soars-to-200-000-on-eu-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加勒比地区的“黄金护照”变得越来越贵，这是对美国和欧盟打击公民身份销售压力的回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/caribbean-golden-passport-cost-soars-to-200-000-on-eu-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:03:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫斯科袭击后俄罗斯考虑收紧移民工人规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/russia-weighs-tighter-migrant-worker-rules-after-moscow-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在塔吉克斯坦国民被指控在首都犯下二十多年来最严重的暴行后，俄罗斯正在考虑进行一系列改革以收紧其移民法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/russia-weighs-tighter-migrant-worker-rules-after-moscow-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 15:43:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
